 ruined it's greatness. You didn't even know what the last boss looked like until you saw her in the very end. The last cutscene made up for it though. FFIX, though it went back to it's oldschool roots, was pretty retarded in my opinion. It had its very good points, like excelent cutscenes, and Vivi (That guy dominated), but I just can't stand the main villain. I also didn't like the fact that your whole party was a band of sideshow freaks (excluding Garnette). Final Fantasy X looked wonderful, and it wasn't a bad game. The story was pretty cool, and it had some interesting characters. However the voice acting, though it was a great try, made me laugh so many times and points where you shouldn't be laughing. Same with the music. The hym of the fayth got so obnoxious I couldn't stand it, and the last boss music was hilarious. It sounded like Ramstein or something. Also, it was a pretty linear. I wasn't a fan of the sphere grid, nor the battle system.<br>
          One game I left out was Final Fantasy Tactics. When I bought that game, I had no idea what it would be like. Then, after I played it for about two days, I thought the game dominated, and then played it for days straight and got everything you could get. The game is worth the fact that you can get Cloud alone. You don't need any other reason. However, there are plenty more reasons why it dominates. The battle system is fun, the class system is f-ing sweet, and the plot is amazing. I guess I'll just have to keep waiting and hoping that they make a game that matches the greatness of FFVII and FFT. If they made a game that rivaled that of those two games, I'd never buy another game again, because that would be all I need. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#CCCCCC><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub25.ezboard.com/bpolykarbonbbs.showLocalUserPublicProfile?login=prismrefraction>PrismRefraction</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Karbonite</span><br> <font color=#336699>(8/12/02 5:38:29 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub25.ezboard.com/fpolykarbonbbsfrm32.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=231.topic&index=70>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> <img src="http://www.ezboard.com/images/posticons/pi_exclamation_mark.gif" align=absmiddle>  Re: shiggity shiggity shwa</span><hr size=1> What system is Tactics for? <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#aaaaaa><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub25.ezboard.com/uohhenry18.showPublicProfile?language=EN>ohhenry18</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/wink.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Karbonite</span><br> <font color=#336699>(8/12/02 7:50:20 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub25.ezboard.com/fpolykarbonbbsfrm32.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=231.topic&index=71>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://persondoi